{"tid":1878812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警察招募日】銀行職員請假考督察：警方應好好經營形象","createTime":"2020-02-13T21:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T05:38:41.000Z","uid":297241,"like":10,"dislike":861,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"e7aba8c2761f81e790babeda0fba4a85d064a6ab","tid":1878812,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T21:57:48.000Z","msg":"【警察招募日】銀行職員請假考督察：<br />\n警方應好好經營形象<br />\n<br />\n香港警務處今日（12日）舉行冬季招募日，招募警員、督察及輔警。<br />\n<br />\n有投考輔警的應徵者表示，「都係搵多份錢。」亦有銀行業職員特意請假投考督察，並指<span style=\"color: red;\">警務處和一般公司一樣，需好好經營在市民心目中的形象。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方今日(12日)舉行冬季招募日，吸引不少年輕人投考。現時從事金融行業的梁先生打算投考輔警，並直言「都係想搵多份錢。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2315312/org/dcdfd8a056f2ed2c8625b4821fe188b4.jpg/Algqs7RlWl3LeU1_e0DTMXri9ixi9WufJJQcsCSUHLA?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2315312%2Forg%2Fdcdfd8a056f2ed2c8625b4821fe188b4.jpg%2FAlgqs7RlWl3LeU1_e0DTMXri9ixi9WufJJQcsCSUHLA%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=9c2420e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警隊今日（一月十二日）在警察總部舉辦冬季「警察招募日」。招募日為有志投身警隊的人士提供一站式服務，縮短遴選時間。（政府新聞處）</span>"},{"pid":"7a317c62caf0bc2c17963c78676dd382ee4be11e","tid":1878812,"uid":3241,"like":978,"dislike":5,"score":973,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T22:02:41.000Z","msg":"呢段時間去做狗嘅人<br />\n人格可見係亳無廉恥，道德水平奇低嘅人渣"},{"pid":"c437524d1811b7c312ed0bf36912df56562f8031","tid":1878812,"uid":227271,"like":155,"dislike":2,"score":153,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T22:05:17.000Z","msg":"入黎認人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f884dfcbb29b54dbba0f63291cfea171c4d6c470","tid":1878812,"uid":8410,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T22:09:59.000Z","msg":"好撚無恥"},{"pid":"f00f31dacfbe4d43bc1abb702847ee0a20f7317b","tid":18788